n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nplot(0:20, ARMAacf(ar = 0.8, lag.max = 20), type = \"h\")\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](rtp_exercises_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-20-1.png){width=672}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n\n### D\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\ntheo_pacf <- ARMAacf(ar = c(0.5, 0.2), lag.max = 100, pacf = TRUE)\nsim_data <- arima.sim(model = list(ar = c(0.5, 0.2)), n = 500)\nestim_pacf <- pacf(sim_data, lag.max = 100, plot = FALSE)$acf\n\nplot(1:100, theo_pacf, type = \"h\", ylim = c(-0.1, 0.6))\nlines(1:100, estim_pacf, type = \"l\")\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](rtp_exercises_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-21-1.png){width=672}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n\n## Exercise 4.2\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\ndata <- read.table(\"/home/nils/dev/mscids-notes/fs26/rtp/data/kreatin.dat\", header=TRUE)\ndata\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\n      n gehalt\n1     1     70\n2     2     70\n3     3     70\n4     4     69\n5     5     71\n6     6     68\n7     7     70\n8     8     65\n9     9     69\n10   10     70\n11   11     70\n12   12     68\n13   13     65\n14   14     75\n15   15     72\n16   16     75\n17   17     70\n18   18     70\n19   19     70\n20   20     75\n21   21     70\n22   22     72\n23   23     75\n24   24     68\n25   25     75\n26   26     73\n27   27     76\n28   28     70\n29   29     70\n30   30     70\n31   31     70\n32   32     71\n33   33     70\n34   34     71\n35   35     75\n36   36     71\n37   37     72\n38   38     71\n39   39     68\n40   40     70\n41   41     70\n42   42     68\n43   43     69\n44   44     70\n45   45     68\n46   46     69\n47   47     70\n48   48     65\n49   49     68\n50   50     68\n51   51     65\n52   52     65\n53   53     65\n54   54     70\n55   55     68\n56   56     70\n57   57     68\n58   58     69\n59   59     70\n60   60     68\n61   61     69\n62   62     71\n63   63     68\n64   64     70\n65   65     70\n66   66     69\n67   67  